snippet.title: Memórias Afogadas - Trailer(En)
snippet.description:
A game that takes place in the late 1950s, when was builting the federal capital of Brazil, Brasília. Based on real events, the game tells the story of one of the largest workers' villages called Amaury Village, which was flooded by the waters of the artificial lake Paranoá.
